Name: Cat's Eye Brooch
AttributesDescription: A Cat's Eye brooch from Carlotta, reflecting your golden eyes—also a personal token from her.
BgDescription: In Montelli, each member has an item corresponding to their code name. Carlotta might begin preparing this gift for you from the very moment she was captivated by your golden eyes and offered you the code name "Cat's Eye." Although you don't intend to officially join Montelli, you know that she will forever keep this code name for you—Cat's Eye, the first and only member to receive Opal's personal invitation.
ObtainedShowDescription: A Cat's Eye brooch from Carlotta.
